snippet.title: Tanggal - Official Trailer (2018)
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE FOR FREE.

Brave the darkness to find a way out, as well as explore the environment to find all the pieces of the story and figure out the mystery behind it all...

Tanggal is a first-person atmospheric horror game, inspired by Filipino mythology.

Itch.io: https://isipgames.itch.io/tanggal
Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/tanggal/343028
